OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with sunny spells and
OL,6,Fpatchy cloud on Monday morning. Cloud
OL,7,Flifting and breaking through the
OL,8,Fafternoon to leave more lengthy
OL,9,Fsunshine. Feeling pleasantly warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and fine end to the day
OL,12,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine.
OL,13,FStaying dry overnight with clear
OL,14,Fspells, some patchy cloud and light
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FContinuing largely fine, dry
OL,18,Fand settled, some thicker cloud around
OL,19,Fat times, perhaps with the odd spot of
OL,20,Fdrizzle over the Lake District.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
